{"tid":2008041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］林鄭：市民及國際社會早晚會知道香港警隊是卓越","createTime":"2020-05-08T17:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T03:22:55.000Z","uid":46906,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"19ea50adc13c8fd600094b5f58f331d9c6e53725","tid":2008041,"uid":46906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:25:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">2019年12月31日 21:59</span>&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥到訪灣仔警察總部，了解警方為前線提供的膳食安排，並為前線人員打氣，又指，全港市民及國際社會早晚會知道香港警隊是卓越，以及是政府最大的資產之一。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥：「我們亦相信，正義永遠站在我們這邊，儘管現在仍然很困難。我知道鄧炳強上任後，真的是不眠不休，我相信這些努力。全港的市民，甚至國際上現在被蒙蔽，批評警隊的人士，他們早晚都會知道，香港這支卓越的警隊是香港特別行政區最大的資產之一。我可以對大家說，我在述職期間，習近平主席亦是公開表示對大家的支持，私下很多中央官員都對大家表示敬意，不要說是十四億人，是大家的後盾。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知喇知喇，犯罪成績卓越呀嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9816e9e5b49f962037aebcb87ae8c635aa10839","tid":2008041,"uid":104804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:27:36.000Z","msg":"犯法來自情操高尚是卓越"},{"pid":"c9eba9250fa8843acf8dc9548d1b32055fcdf51b","tid":2008041,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:28:16.000Z","msg":"情操極度高尚嘅犯罪集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328d862981aca5e86e2ed257bab06ef1e4ef0a63","tid":2008041,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T19:47:45.000Z","msg":"資產呀, 聽到未? 必要時可以賣"},{"pid":"6bd58098406b941bdceec5f9607140963aede70e","tid":2008041,"uid":356914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T19:51:01.000Z","msg":"點解佢樣樣野都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69331fef2f16e914a3ad6d2a3441c6357ab649a2","tid":2008041,"uid":129924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T19:52:19.000Z","msg":"其實我都一早知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009706ab323b0db5b002443acd3e8dfc48a408c0","tid":2008041,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:22:55.000Z","msg":"係犯法方面, 的確係好卓越, 真係不愧係國家認証的恐怖分子集團 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}